From 0000000000000000000000000000000000000000 Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: Codex <codex@openai.com>
Date: Sat, 7 Mar 2026 23:59:00 -0300
Subject: [PATCH] meson: stop installing vendored gnim

Fedora packages `gnim` separately. AGS should keep looking for it in
`/usr/share/ags/js/node_modules/gnim`, but it should not try to install a
vendored copy from the AGS source tree.
---
 meson.build | 5 -----
 1 file changed, 5 deletions(-)

diff --git a/meson.build b/meson.build
index 8226b2d..e8f7194 100644
--- a/meson.build
+++ b/meson.build
@@ -13,11 +13,6 @@ install_subdir(
   install_dir: pkgdatadir / 'js',
 )
 
-install_subdir(
-  'node_modules/gnim',
-  install_dir: pkgdatadir / 'js/node_modules',
-)
-
 custom_target(
   'cli',
   command: [
-- 
